This privacy policy applies to the website CONference, operated by [company name]. At CONference, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is safe and secure. This policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use and protect that information, and your rights and choices with respect to your personal information.

content.text: When you use CONference, we may collect certain personal information that you provide to us, such as your name, email address, phone number, and other contact information. We may also collect information about your education, employment history, skills, and experience, as well as any other information you choose to provide in your profile or job applications.

We use the information we collect to provide our services, including matching job seekers with potential employers and facilitating the application process. We may also use your information to communicate with you, provide customer support, and improve our services.

We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in providing our services, such as email and hosting providers. We may also share your information with employers who have job openings that match your skills and experience. However, we will never share your information with third parties for marketing purposes without your consent.
